{"tid":595212,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（噁心到極點了）有冇人好鍾意鼠類動物？","createTime":"2018-03-16T12:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T13:12:30.000Z","uid":90457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec6d43b37b3e3af24fdcbb626a792da75f4717a","tid":595212,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"有時半夜落屋企樓下食煙（暗角位影響唔到人，儘管詛咒）不時見到啲老鼠出嚟搵食，有次見過兩隻老鼠bb走出嚟，大唔過我手掌心好細粒好得意，跑又跑唔郁，似係啱啱出齊啲毛<br />\n一見到我就想走，一隻走得甩，另外一隻又戇尻尻咁，明明係平地，我一腳擋住佢去路，佢連兜路都唔識就走返轉頭，我第二隻腳塞住佢退路佢又走返轉頭，咁樣俾我撚足兩分鐘來回尻行都逃走唔到，傻到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰刻開始我呢世人唔再討厭老鼠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係驚佢周身病毒，我真係會捉返屋企養！"},{"pid":"c885081b3a4f3952c863f5eae46b23b073e1b8cf","tid":595212,"uid":166301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"9f2295ea6b0aaa036bec6377ca58f87ac0f9bcf5","tid":595212,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c885081b3a4f3952c863f5eae46b23b073e1b8cf","tid":595212,"uid":166301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"比着係成年老鼠我唔會留情，見到係bb變咗大愛撚，玩完放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eeefa458a32d9f5328cdbd86ad57d1a8b8b35f6","tid":595212,"uid":32980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"Pigmy"},{"pid":"7057c1fb8b2c60ccccb7a9001fb261338dfccedc","tid":595212,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"浸酒真係一流"},{"pid":"b30a5f6f63e3860150a4a148fdc023effb19d337","tid":595212,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7057c1fb8b2c60ccccb7a9001fb261338dfccedc","tid":595212,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"浸酒真係一流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime